7 TRIGGER / Yoh Yoshinari / \"Little Witch Academia\" Committee \u00a9 UNIVRS, Inc.", "short_description": "Soar through the skies, hunt for ghosts, and become the best witch racer in the world!\n\n\u00a9 2017 T/YY/LWAC   \u00a9 UNIV"}, {"images": {"nodes": [{"file_name": "Squere_JP_202012.png", "id": "1327244154279833", "image_type": "APP_IMG_COVER_SQUARE", "uri": "https://scontent-iad3-2.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/38982648_1327244157613166_2961322866020914640_n.png?_nc_cat=109&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=vF3x_uXxzycQ7kNvgE_ohwf&_nc_ht=scontent-iad3-2.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYDBlp4uixFQ9IWrL8Nr-OBGfaCf-KQVBef9xKFBEd7yvA&oe=670A760E"}, {"file_name": "mini_JP_202012.png", "id": "767739813819324", "image_type": "APP_IMG_SMALL_LANDSCAPE", "uri": "https://scontent-iad3-2.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/38974453_767739817152657_5763260574459999295_n.png?_nc_cat=109&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=bxtMucvEJDUQ7kNvgEMKnAD&_nc_ht=scontent-iad3-2.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYDLIYEqv1ThcD2fX3lntxu2Tzh2Aok--cSGojVQH0h4yw&oe=670A60E6"}, {"file_name": "Portrait_JP_202012.png", "id": "687368831924916", "image_type": "APP_IMG_COVER_PORTRAIT", "uri": "https://scontent-iad3-2.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/38974557_687368835258249_3301610840483328822_n.png?_nc_cat=109&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=wco5aErzBZEQ7kNvgEC5b2F&_nc_ht=scontent-iad3-2.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYCVK3MbbLUas5l7Ho80qg-w0Qu0tVWT_-4CbzI1DHEl6Q&oe=670A5333"}, {"file_name": "Landscape_JP_202012.png", "id": "210773470635130", "image_type": "APP_IMG_COVER_LANDSCAPE", "uri": "https://scontent-iad3-2.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/39001687_210773473968463_5238021041892551677_n.png?_nc_cat=105&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=huBhDiDj7a8Q7kNvgH-6Y3a&_nc_ht=scontent-iad3-2.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYCOh_ejOU0wrOUMGZc9p8ahEnIrCUAsZyTsH0rvWYOnTw&oe=670A634F"}, {"file_name": "HERO_JP_202012.png", "id": "136977781532024", "image_type": "APP_IMG_HERO", "uri": "https://scontent-iad3-1.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/38974450_136977784865357_8309174075716611